summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the sale of City real property for multifamily development; authorizing the sale of Dearborn-Hiawatha Parcel 2 a & b in the I-90 Redevelopment Project area at Hiawatha Place South and South Charles Street to HomeSight or its designee; authorizing the Director of the Office of Housing to execute, deliver, and administer the contract for sale of land, deed and related documents; and ratifying and confirming prior acts.
